AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 1302* House Bill No. 1317
by deleting all language after the enacting clause and substituting:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 55-10-402(f)(1), is amended by
deleting the subdivision and substituting:
(1) The sentencing court shall determine when an offender sentenced to a
period of incarceration for a violation of § 55-10-401 is required to commence service of
the sentence.
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
